window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A fantasy romance that will spirit you away. Perfect for fans of </b><b><i>Gild</i></b><b> and </b><b><i>The Never King</i></b><b>.</b></p> <p>Peter Pan has stolen me away to Neverland.</p> <p>He's not the child of legend. Instead, he's a man who vows to protect me from the villainous Hook. I stay with Peter and his Lost Boys, safe in the wilds of the island.</p> <p>But Hook is searching for me. And when his pirates find me, the black-hearted pirate king will claim me for his own.</p> <p><b>Lily's Note: This book begins the Never and Night Series, a slow-burn fantasy romance. Please mind the cliff. </b></p>"; 
